extends layout.pug

block content 
  article.grid-container.portfolio-intro
    div
      h3 To Learn and solve real world problems are my passions.
      //- Add a title or heading like My Portfolio, or Hey, Potential Employers, or Let's make the web great together! 
      h4 My Portfolio.

      //- Add a description for your portfolio, what this project is, it's purpose, what it's supposed to accomplish, etc. 
      p.lead.text-light
        | In this portfolio I showcased some of my best projects I have built as a Full Stack JavaScript Developer. With these projects, am seeking for a job where I can work and learn new Technologies and to improve my skills as a great Developer.
  article.grid-container.portfolio-index
    

    .grid-x.grid-margin-x.small-up-2.medium-up-2.large-up-3

      each project in projects
        .cell
          a(href=`/projects/${project.id}`)
            img.thumbnail(src=`${project.image_urls[0]}`)
            h5 #{project.project_name}


      




          
      
